SECURITY NOTICE:

This plugin has been designed with security in mind:
- No PHP eval() or exec() usage
- No SQL injection vulnerabilities
- All user inputs are sanitized
- CSRF protection via nonces
- Proper capability checks

For security issues, please report via GitHub:
https://github.com/engmuhammednasser/custom-currency-icon-for-woocommerce/security/advisories
